    <string name="instruction_futoshiki">Each row &amp; column must contain 1&#8211;%1$d. Honor the &lt; &gt; inequalities.</string>
    <string name="instruction_hidato">Fill 1&#8211;%1$d. Each next number must touch the previous (incl. diagonals).</string>
    <string name="instruction_kakuro">Tap a white cell, then a digit. Runs must sum to the clue with no repeats.</string>
    <string name="instruction_lights_out">Tap a light to toggle it and its neighbors. Turn all OFF!</string>
    <string name="instruction_mastermind">Tap a slot then a color. &#9679; = right color &amp; spot, &#9675; = right color, wrong spot.</string>
    <string name="instruction_nonogram">Tap = fill &#9632;   Long-press = mark &#10005;</string>
    <string name="instruction_nurikabe">Tap to shade. Each number forms a white island of exactly that size. All shaded cells must connect. No 2&#215;2 shaded.</string>
    <string name="instruction_skyscraper">Use numbers 1&#8211;%1$d. Each row &amp; column must contain every number. Outside numbers = visible buildings from that side.</string>
    <string name="instruction_slitherlink">Tap an edge to toggle. Numbers = edges around that cell. All edges form one closed loop.</string>
